<template>
  <v-card tile>
    <v-list dense>
      <v-subheader>Deine WÃ¶rterlisten</v-subheader>

<script>
export default {
  props: ['entrys'],
  watch:{
    selectedItem:{
      handler(){
        this.$emit("selected-item", this.selectedItem)
      }
    }
  },
  data(){
    return{
      selectedItem: null,
      items: [],
    }   
  }
}
  
</script>
